ete%20with%20rainbow%20sprinkles.%20Regardless%20of%20cost%2C%20I've%20discovered%20that%20food%20is%20how%20people%20express%20themselves%2C%20their%20country's%20history%2C%20and%20traditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20exploring%20Panama%2C%20trying%20local%20cuisines%20and%20ingredients%20was%20top%20of%20mind%2C%20so%20I%20kicked%20things%20off%20with%20a%20chef's%20selection%20menu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bar%20at%20Intimo%20Restaurante.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6643aaf19686a6f37bffc84d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bar%20at%20Intimo%20Restaurante.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2228890590-c546-4f14-910b-10fc240fe77f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20restaurant's%20dishes%20highlighted%20local%20ingredients%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20its%20name%2C%20Intimo%20Restaurante%20is%20intimate.%20There%20are%20only%20three%20tables%2C%20a%20small%20outdoor%20patio%2C%20and%20a%20long%20chef's%20bar.%20In%20total%2C%20the%20restaurant%20accommodates%2028%20diners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sat%20at%20the%20bar%2C%20and%20moments%20after%20getting%20settled%2C%20the%20restaurant's%20bartender%20introduced%20himself%20and%20asked%20me%20what%20I%20would%20like%20to%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20explained%20that%20the%20restaurant%20didn't%20have%20a%20bar%20menu.%20Instead%2C%20there%20was%20a%20selection%20of%20wines%20and%20liquors.%20He%20could%20make%20me%20a%20traditional%20cocktail%2C%20or%20I%20could%20tell%20him%20my%20preferences%2C%20and%20he%20would%20create%20a%20personalized%20drink%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20sharing%20that%20I'd%20like%20something%20refreshing%20and%20a%20bit%20tart%2C%20a%20lychee%20cocktail%20appeared%20in%20front%20of%20me.%20I%20never%20would've%20requested%20it%2C%20but%20it%20was%20exactly%20what%20I%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20custom%20cocktail%20at%20the%20Intimo%20Restaurante.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6643aaf1b4abc992e8c96b4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20custom%20cocktail%20at%20the%20Intimo%20Restaurante.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20the%20restaurant's%20chef%2C%20Carlos%20%26quot%3BChombol%C3%ADn%26quot%3B%20Alba%2C%20stopped%20by%20to%20introduce%20himself%2C%20welcome%20me%20to%20Intimo%2C%20and%20ask%20if%20I%20had%20any%20food%20allergies%2C%20something%20he%20does%20for%20every%20guest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20explained%20that%20Intimo%20serves%20traditional%20Panamanian%20ingredients%20that%20are%20often%20creatively%20reimagined%20in%20dishes.%20He%20said%2090%25%20of%20the%20restaurant's%20ingredients%20are%20locally%20sourced%2C%20which%20means%20the%20menu%20changes%20throughout%20the%20year%20to%20highlight%20peak%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlba%20walked%20me%20through%20the%20menu%20and%20outlined%20the%20evening's%20chef's%20section%2C%20which%20includes%20five%20small%20plates%20from%20the%20menu.%20It%20was%20what%20I%20planned%20on%20ordering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20he%20mentioned%20tartare%2C%20and%20my%20heart%20sank.%20I%20typically%20eat%20a%20pescatarian%20diet%2C%20and%20while%20I%20sometimes%20try%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-eat-pescatarian-diet-except-when-traveling-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeat%20dishes%20when%20traveling%20to%20new%20countries%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20tartare%20isn't%20something%20I%20can%20currently%20get%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20Alba%20said%20he%20could%20swap%20the%20tartare%20for%20another%20dish.%20He%20offered%20a%20shrimp%20substitute%2C%20which%20I%20happily%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sat%20back%20and%20watched%20the%20kitchen%20staff%20create%20dishes%20for%20the%20two%20dozen%20guests%20in%20the%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20courses%20of%20the%20chef's%20selection.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6643abe8f27898f532d78736%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESide-by-side%20courses%20of%20the%20chef's%20selection.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20my%20first%20course%20arrived.%20A%20waitress%20walked%20me%20through%20all%20the%20ingredients%20in%20the%20tuna%20dish%2C%20which%20included%20%26quot%3Bpastrami-cured%26quot%3B%20tuna%20in%20leche%20de%20tigre%2C%20a%20Peruvian%20citrus-based%20marinade%20for%20ceviche.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20and%20remained%20the%20high%20point%20of%20the%20night%20for%20me.%20The%20tuna%20was%20fresh%2C%20and%20a%20crispy%2C%20crunchy%20corn%20garnish%20was%20the%20perfect%20texture%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20was%20the%20shrimp%20crudo%2C%20followed%20by%20grilled%20tomatoes%20from%20Panama's%20Boquete%20region.%20The%20main%20dish%20was%20octopus%20guacho%2C%20a%20traditional%20Panamanian%20dish%20complemented%20with%20Caribbean%20sofrito.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20a%20dessert%20mousse%20paired%20with%20amaretto%20ice%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20service%20was%20timed%20flawlessly.%20I%20didn't%20feel%20rushed%2C%20but%20I%20wasn't%20longing%20for%20my%20next%20meal.%20Plus%2C%20an%20open%20kitchen%20meant%20I%20got%20to%20watch%20each%20dish%20being%20crafted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22651a79c6-a86f-4e8b-9258-386c8d752b25%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAs%20a%20solo%20traveler%2C%20it's%20also%20the%20ideal%20opportunity%20to%20try%20multiple%20dishes%20in%20one%20sitting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20having%20someone%20to%20share%20appetizers%2C%20mains%2C%20and%20dessert%20with%20is%20easily%20my%20least%20favorite%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-dine-alone-tips-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epart%20about%20dining%20alone%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20I%20want%20to%20try%20as%20many%20dishes%20as%20possible%2C%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20waste%20food%20and%20simply%20don't%20always%20have%20the%20space%20in%20my%20stomach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tasting%20menu%20was%20a%20great%20way%20to%20solve%20this%20dilemma.%20Since%20each%20dish%20was%20smaller%20than%20the%20typical%20portion%2C%20I%20saved%20money%2C%20didn't%20waste%20food%2C%20and%20had%20just%20enough%20room%20to%20polish%20off%20all%20five%20plates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20a%20tasting%20menu%20took%20the%20stress%20out%20of%20ordering.%20I%20spend%20far%20too%20long%20eyeing%20menus%2C%20debating%20what%20dishes%20to%20try%2C%20and%20leaving%20with%20regrets%20over%20what%20I%20did%20and%20didn't%20pick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20admit%20that%20not%20every%20course%20on%20Intimo's%20tasting%20menu%20catered%20to%20my%20preferences%3B%20next%20time%2C%20I'll%20order%20the%20bass%20in%20Caribbean%20curry%20over%20the%20guacho.%20But%20the%20tasting%20menu%20encouraged%20me%20to%20try%20new%20dishes%20that%20I%20may%20not%20have%20ordered%20on%20my%20own%2C%20and%20thankfully%2C%20most%20dishes%2C%20like%20the%20roasted%20tomatoes%2C%20left%20my%20tastebuds%20happily%20surprised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltogether%2C%20the%20meal%20cost%20%2483%20with%20a%20tip.%20For%20me%2C%20that's%20a%20splurge%2C%20but%20it%20was%20worth%20every%20penny.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20restaurant's%20staff%20was%20welcoming%2C%20which%20was%20a%20lovely%20introduction%20to%20meeting%20Panamanians.%20The%20ingredients%20were%20fresh%2C%20the%20ideal%20way%20to%20learn%20about%20a%20region.%20And%20the%20meals%20were%20delicious%2C%20which%20was%20a%20great%20kickoff%20to%20the%20next%20eight%20days%20of%20dining%20across%20Panama.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20