ews%2Fwebqoof%2Frahul-gandhi-sonia-gandhi-jesus-picture-fact-check%23read-more%5C%22%3EThe%20Quint%3C%2Fa%3E%20revealed%20that%20it%20is%20a%20painting%20titled%20%26quot%3BMadonna%20Oriflamma%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20a%20few%20facts%20about%20the%20%26quot%3BMadonna%20Oriflamma%26quot%3B%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMadonna%20Oriflamma%20is%20a%201932%20painting%20by%20Russian%20painter%20Nicholas%20Roerich.%20The%20painting%20features%20a%20person%20holding%20a%20banner%20with%20three%20red%20dots%2C%20surrounded%20by%20a%20red%20circle.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fsvdejala.blogspot.com%2F2017%2F08%2Fcozumel-one-circle-three-red-dots.html%5C%22%3ENicholas%20Roerich%3C%2Fa%3E%20created%20the%20painting%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20human%20unity%20and%20called%20the%20geometrical%20art%20the%20%26quot%3BBanner%20of%20Peace%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERussian%20painter%20and%20writer%20Nicholas%20Roerich%2C%20aka%20Nikolai%20Konstantinovich%20Rerikh%2C%20was%20born%20in%201874.%20Throughout%20his%20career%2C%20he%20has%20involved%20himself%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.roerich.org%2Froerich-pact.php%5C%22%3Eproblems%20of%20cultural%20preservation.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThis%20original%20art%20is%20on%20display%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fshop.amorc.org.au%2Fproducts%2Fmadonna-oriflamma-poster%3Fvariant%3D43440545956066%5C%22%3ENicholas%20Roerich%20Museum%20in%20New%20York%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20per%20the%20official%20Nicholas%20Roerich's%20website%2C%20the%20painting%20has%20been%20on%20loan%20to%20the%20museum%20since%201960.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThis%20Banner%20of%20Peace%20emblem%20was%20integral%20to%20the%20Roerich%20Pact%2C%20an%20international%20treaty%20initiated%20by%20Roerich%2C%20aimed%20at%20protecting%20cultural%20artefacts%20during%20times%20of%20war%E2%80%8B%20and%20conflict.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20off