E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGot%20a%20question%20for%20our%20columnist%3F%20Write%20to%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%20using%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cNtGiwNUd-6vLAYAc75grvly3C10-854vFP4arw%2Fviewform%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cNtGiwNUd-6vLAYAc75grvly3C10-854vFP4arw%2Fviewform%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22summary_bullets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20Google%20form%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDear%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20have%20four%20kids%20between%20the%20ages%20of%20four%20and%2010%2C%20and%20we%20spend%20every%20weekend%20at%20a%20series%20of%20birthday%20parties.%20We%20have%20gone%20to%20zoo%20birthdays%2C%20skating%20rinks%2C%20trampoline%20parks%2C%20nature%20reserves%2C%20and%20people's%20backyards.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20food%2C%20when%20offered%2C%20is%20nearly%20always%20Costco%20pizza%20or%20hotdogs%2C%20but%20usually%2C%20it's%20just%20a%20cake%20the%20kids'%20parents%20bought%20from%20the%20supermarket.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20entry%20is%20at%20least%20a%20%2425%20gift.%20This%20isn't%20bad%20for%20one%20party%2C%20but%20with%20four%20kids%2C%20it%20can%20get%20as%20high%20as%20%24100%20to%20%24200%20a%20weekend.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20my%20kids'%20birthday%20parties%2C%20it%20is%20very%20clear%20that%20our%20invitee's%20presence%20is%20the%20only%20present%20we%20want.%20I%20don't%20need%2020%20new%20pieces%20of%20junk%20introduced%20to%20our%20home%20four%20times%20a%20year%20anyway%20%E2%80%94%20where%20would%20we%20put%20it%20all%3F%20I%20don't%20understand%20why%20other%20parents%20would%20want%20it.%20I%20can't%20afford%20the%20financial%20burden%20of%20birthday%20party%20gifts%2C%20especially%20when%20my%20kids%20aren't%20even%20getting%20a%20nutritious%20meal!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20I%20also%20don't%20want%20my%20kids%20to%20miss%20out%20on%20the%20fun%20or%20be%20the%20reason%20some%20poor%20kid%20doesn't%20have%20any%20friends%20attend%20their%20birthday%20party.%20How%20do%20I%20save%20money%20without%20feeling%20like%20a%20spoilsport%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBurned%20Out%20on%20Birthdays%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDear%20Burned%20Out%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20mother%20of%20three%20elementary%20and%20middle%20school%20kids%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-write-advice-column-relationships-and-money-2024-3%5C%22%3EI%20relate%20to%20your%20struggle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20am%20all%20for%20inviting%20every%20kid%20in%20class%20to%20birthday%20parties.%20I%20don't%20think%20anyone%20should%20feel%20left%20out%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%204th%20graders%20can%20handle%20the%20social%20power%20of%20picking%20and%20choosing%20who%20gets%20an%20invite%20and%20who%20doesn't.%20However%2C%20this%20popular%20rule%20also%20means%20my%20kids%20receive%20over%20a%20dozen%20birthday%20party%20invitations%20each%20school%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20doesn't%20include%20the%20invitations%20they%20receive%20from%20cousins%2C%20church%20friends%2C%20neighbors%2C%20and%20best%20friends%20who%20moved%20schools%20or%20are%20in%20a%20different%20class%20this%20year.%20At%20%2425%20a%20pop%2C%20the%20simple%20joy%20of%20attending%20a%20buddy's%20birthday%20could%20cost%20us%20well%20into%20the%20thousands.%20And%20you%20have%20one%20kid%20more%20than%20me.%20You're%20not%20crazy%20for%20feeling%20like%20this%20is%20becoming%20a%20financial%20burden.%20However%2C%20I%20am%20here%20to%20tell%20you%20that%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20give%20up%20on%20sticking%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-budgeting-apps%5C%22%3Ebudget%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20remember%20that%20just%20because%20your%20kids%20get%20invited%20to%20every%20birthday%20party%20doesn't%20mean%20you're%20obligated%20to%20take%20them.%20If%20your%20kids%20are%20anything%20like%20mine%2C%20how%20close%20they%20are%20to%20the%20birthday%20kid%20has%20little%20to%20do%20with%20whether%20they%20want%20to%20spend%20the%20afternoon%20bouncing%20their%20brains%20out%20at%20a%20trampoline%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%2C%20my%20kids'%20response%20to%20a%20party%20invite%20will%20always%20be%20yes.%20But%20mine%20isn't.%20As%20overwhelming%20as%20children's%20birthday%20parties%20can%20be%20financially%2C%20they're%20also%20quite%20a%20time%20drain.%20As%20my%20children%20get%20older%2C%20drop-off%20parties%20are%20thankfully%20becoming%20the%20norm%2C%20but%20I%20still%20have%20a%20second%20grader%2C%20and%20expecting%20anyone%20to%20babysit%20a%20bunch%20of%208-year-olds%20hopped%20up%20on%20Kool-Aid%2C%20cake%2C%20and%20laser%20tag%20feels%20unfair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20I%20limit%20my%20kids%20to%20only%20attending%20the%20parties%20of%20close%20friends%2C%20family%20members%2C%20kids%20I%20suspect%20may%20not%20have%20many%20friends%2C%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20epic-level%20parties%20my%20kids%20beg%20me%20to%20attend.%20Overall%2C%20we%20attend%20five%20to%20ten%20parties%20a%20year%20for%20each%20kid%20%E2%80%94%20still%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20spread%20out%20over%20the%20course%20of%20a%20year%2C%20it's%20not%20too%20bad%20time-wise.%20The%20expense%2C%20however%2C%20still%20creeps%20up%20on%20us%2C%20so%20I%20also%20draw%20a%20boundary%20across%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20wrote%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bcost%20of%20entry%20is%20a%20%2425%20gift.%26quot%3B%20Is%20that%20true%2C%20though%3F%20I%20have%20never%20seen%20a%20birthday%20invitation%20party%20with%20a%20minimum%20gift%20price%20specified.%20As%20a%20mom%2C%20however%2C%20I%20am%20familiar%20with%20the%20unwritten%20rule%20you%20are%20referring%20to.%20I%20recently%20saw%20a%20meme%20on%20social%20media%20joking%20that%20kids'%20birthday%20parties%20are%20just%20parents%20passing%20around%20the%20same%20%2425%20over%20and%20over%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20laugh%20because%20it's%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20you%20can%20opt%20out%20of%20feeling%20like%20you%20need%20to%20hit%20a%20certain%20dollar%20amount.%20We%20should%20stop%20looking%20at%20birthday%20parties%20as%20transactional.%20You%20mentioned%20the%20low-quality%20dinners%20typically%20provided%20at%20these%20events.%20I%20know%20I've%20complained%20a%20few%20times%20when%20the%20only%20food%20offered%20at%20parties%20scheduled%20during%20traditional%20meal%20times%20are%20chips%20and%20cupcakes.%20But%20in%20reality%2C%20they%20aren't%20obligated%20to%20feed%20our%20kids%20any%20more%20than%20we're%20obligated%20to%20bring%20a%20%2425%20present.%20There%20is%20no%20entry%20price%20because%20it's%20a%20free%20event%2C%20and%20you%20can't%20complain%20about%20a%20free%20event%20you%20chose%20to%20attend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20my%20hack%20for%20keeping%20our%20birthday%20present%20budget%20small%3A%20Kids%20like%20money.%20It%20makes%20them%20feel%20grown%20up%20and%20powerful.%20Give%20them%20three%20%245%20bills%2C%20and%20they'll%20feel%20flush%20with%20cash.%20Give%20them%20a%20%2410%20bill%2C%20and%20they%20won't%20think%2C%20%26quot%3BReally%3F%20Only%20%2410%2C%3Cem%3E%20in%20this%20econom%3C%2Fem%3Ey%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey'll%20simply%20tally%20it%20up%20with%20all%20the%20cash%20they%20got%20from%20their%20grandparents%2C%20aunts%2C%20uncles%2C%20and%20their%20allowance%20and%20come%20up%20with%20that%20magic%20number%20that%20makes%20them%20feel%20like%20the%20richest%20kid%20in%20town.%20Meanwhile%2C%20their%20parents%20will%20be%20pleased%20not%20to%20have%20more%20junk%20headed%20toward%20their%20kid's%20already%20disastrous%20bedroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20option%20is%20to%20shop%20for%20gifts%20at%20dollar%20stores%20like%20Five%20Below%20and%20Dollar%20Tree.%20You%20can%20easily%20assemble%20a%20decent%20craft%20kit%20for%20under%20%2410%20at%20those%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERemember%2C%20in%20many%20ways%20we%20really%20are%20just%20exchanging%20the%20same%20gift%20money%20with%20other%20parents%20over%20and%20over.%20So%2C%20what%20goes%20around%20will%20come%20around%2C%20and%20the%20families%20you%20show%20up%20for%20today%20will%20be%20the%20same%20families%20who%20make%20your%20kids'%20birthdays%20great%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERooting%20for%20you%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELooking%20for%20advice%20on%20how%20your%20savings%2C%20debt%2C%20or%20another%20financial%20challenge%20is%20affecting%20your%20relationships%3F%20Write%20to%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%20using%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cNtGiwNUd-6vLAYAc75grvly3C10-854vFP4arw%2Fviewform%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ethis%20Google%20form%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-find-financial-advisor%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20financial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20hard.%20SmartAsset's%20free%20tool%20matches%20you%20with%20up%20to%20three%20fiduciary%20financial%20advisors%20that%20serve%20your%20area%20in%20minutes.%20Each%20advisor%20has%20been%20vetted%20by%20SmartAsset%20and%20is%20held%20to%20a%20fiduciary%20standard%20to%20act%20in%20your%20best%20interests.%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blan