0%94%20but%20following%20a%20merger%20this%20year%20with%20Eqlipse%20Technologies%2C%20Blue%20Halo%20is%20fast%20approaching%20%241%20billion%20in%20revenue%20and%20has%202%2C400%20employees%20across%2011%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20contracts%20keep%20flowing%20in.%20This%20week%2C%20it%20secured%20a%20%2495.4%20million%20contract%20with%20the%20Space%20and%20Missile%20Defense%20Command%20(SMDC)%20to%20develop%20prototype%20directed%20energy%20(DE)%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blue%20Halo%20CEO%20Jonathan%20Moneymaker%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664499079686a6f37bfffc67%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBlue%20Halo%20CEO%20Jonathan%20Moneymaker%3Cp%3EBlue%20Halo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20(DoD)%20has%20slowly%20come%20around%20to%20the%20idea%20that%20it%20should%20buy%20commercial%20military%20tech%2C%20numerous%20tech%20startups%20are%20hoping%20to%20follow%20the%20same%20path%2C%20providing%20solutions%20for%20US%20national%20security%20while%20getting%20a%20share%20of%20the%20%24842%20billion%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-defense-military-budget-compared-federal-education-spending-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edefense%20budget%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20experts%20have%20cautioned%20that%20grappling%20with%20the%20legendary%20complexity%20of%20the%20defense%20industry%20makes%20it%20unlike%20entering%20any%20other%20growth%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrimes%20are%20not%20particularly%20innovative%20because%20they%20mastered%20the%20acquisition%20process%20rather%20than%20the%20technology%20process.%20However%2C%20startups%20lack%20a%20couple%20of%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Steve%20Blank%2C%20Professor%20of%20Defense%20tech%20innovation%20at%20Stanford%20and%20creator%20of%20the%20Lean%20Startup%20method%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20typically%20lack%20a%20go-to-market%20strategy%20and%20fail%20to%20understand%20the%20complexity%20of%20getting%20an%20order%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%2C%20said%20Blank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DoD%20buys%20to%20satisfy%20what's%20called%20a%20requirement%2C%20where%20someone%20has%20specifically%20requested%20something.%20Writing%20that%20requirement%20is%20a%20long%20process%20that%20primes%20themselves%20typically%20help%20out%20with%2C%20Blank%20explained.%20Startups%20are%20often%20clueless%20about%20that%20process%20and%20completely%20out%20of%20the%20loop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20comes%20the%20actual%20acquisition%20process%2C%20which%20can%20take%20two%20or%20three%20years%20to%20even%20show%20up%20in%20a%20budget%20%E2%80%94%20a%20problem%20if%20you're%20a%20startup%20in%20need%20of%20a%20flow%20of%20orders%20and%20cash%20to%20satisfy%20your%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20understand%20this%20process%2C%20then%20the%20primes%20tend%20to%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20Blank%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223478%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blue%20Halo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664c43d19fc063e829b31bb4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222119%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBlue%20Halo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20swathe%20of%20Silicon%20Valley%20tech%20firms%20eyeing%20up%20defense%2C%20Blue%20Halo%20has%20its%20roots%20on%20the%20other%20side%20%E2%80%94%20Moneymaker%20has%20spent%20the%20last%2025%20years%20in%20the%20defense%20industry%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20that%20insider%20know-how%20combined%20with%20the%20operational%20speeds%20typical%20of%20the%20tech%20world%20that%20Blue%20Halo%20says%20has%20enabled%20its%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20the%20experience%2C%20know-how%2C%20and%20sophistication%20of%20some%20of%20the%20traditional%20primes%20in%20our%20space%2C%20but%20we%20have%20the%20entrepreneurial%20and%20innovative%20speed%20and%20spirit%20of%20some%20of%20the%20newer%20entrants.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20been%20critical%2C%20said%20Moneymaker%2C%20is%20understanding%20not%20just%20what%20the%20military%20needs%20but%20how%20to%20earn%20the%20trust%20of%20defense%20officials%20and%20navigate%20the%20procurement%20process%20to%20get%20it%20into%20their%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESilicon%20Valley%20is%20facing%20%26quot%3Bsome%20learning%20curves%26quot%3B%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20tech%20companies%20will%20have%20exquisite%20groundbreaking%20technology%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20actually%20what%20the%20military%20needs%2C%20or%20it%20will%20be%20incredibly%20hard%20to%20actually%20field%2C%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKnowing%20where%20it's%20applicable%20and%20where%20it's%20not%20is%20incredibly%20important.%20Frankly%2C%20if%20you%20haven't%20grown%20up%20in%20this%20environment%2C%20sometimes%20that%20just%20takes%20a%20little%20longer%20to%20get%20familiar%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Moneymaker.%20%26quot%3BWe%20listen%20better%20than%20a%20lot%20of%20our%20competition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blue%20Halo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664bcfb59fc063e829b3155d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBlue%20Halo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20factor%20Moneymaker%20sees%20as%20an%20advantage%20is%20Blue%20Halo's%20lack%20of%20Silicon%20Valley%20ego.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20lead%20without%20ego%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Blue%20Halo%20CEO.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20all%20done%20exciting%20things%20in%20our%20careers%2C%20but%20this%20is%20about%20being%20part%20of%20something%20bigger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20its%20industry-i