s%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Song%20and%20her%20husband%20didn't%20enjoy%20the%20hustle%20and%20bustle%20of%20Brickell%20in%20Miami.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66325819ec0c696569ff9449%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESong%20and%20her%20husband%20didn't%20enjoy%20the%20hustle%20and%20bustle%20of%20Brickell%20in%20Miami.%3Cp%3EKofi%20Oliver%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20rented%20a%20car.%20For%20three%20days%2C%20we%20were%20in%20the%20car%20all%20day%2C%20zipping%20around%20Miami%20to%20different%20locations.%20We%20ended%20up%20picking%20Coral%20Gables.%20It's%20a%20very%20family-friendly%20neighborhood%2C%20walkable%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20more%20quiet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20need%20good%20credit%20when%20you%20are%20renting%20a%20place.%20Otherwise%2C%20they%20make%20you%20put%20down%20an%20incredible%20deposit%20amount.%20We%20found%20a%20place%20that%20looked%20at%20a%20balance%20of%20everything%20and%20worked%20with%20us%20on%20a%20deposit%20that%20made%20sense%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20challenge%20for%20me%2C%20though%2C%20which%20we've%20always%20known%2C%20is%20that%20the%20visa%20that%20we%20are%20on%20only%20allows%20me%20to%20live%20in%20the%20US.%20It%20would%20not%20allow%20me%20to%20have%20a%20work%20permit%20and%20to%20make%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20defined%20myself%20by%20my%20career%20success.%20But%20I%20see%20it%20as%20an%20investment%20in%20my%20future%20%E2%80%94%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20will%20make%20me%20happy%20long%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22133e12b7-c128-41e1-aecf-692ebf084af6%5C%22%3EAn%20active%2C%20outdoorsy%20lifestyle%20boosts%20my%20happiness%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20get%20seasonal%20depression%2C%20but%20I%20get%20hit%20hard%20every%20year%20with%20it.%20Last%20year%2C%20in%20Toronto%2C%20was%20particularly%20hard%20for%20me.%20It%20just%20felt%20so%20dark%20and%20gloomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20become%20a%20more%20active%20person%2C%20going%20out%20in%20the%20sun%20and%20playing%20tennis%20and%20golf.%20Not%20that%20you%20can't%20do%20that%20in%20Toronto%2C%20but%20being%20in%20Miami%20removes%20some%20of%20those%20barriers%20because%20of%20how%20naturally%20warm%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20I%20do%2C%20I%20just%20try%20to%20do%20outdoors%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Coral%20Gables%20a%20quieter%2C%20family-oriented%20neighborhood%2C%20according%20to%20Song.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6632584cec0c696569ff94c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECoral%20Gables%20is%20a%20quieter%2C%20family-oriented%20neighborhood%2C%20according%20to%20Song.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Susanna%20Song%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20do%20groceries%20by%20foot%2C%20not%20by%20car.%20We%20take%20long%20walks%20here%2C%20an%20hour%20to%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half.%20My%20husband%20is%20also%20teaching%20me%20how%20to%20play%20tennis.%20Eventually%2C%20once%20we%20have%20a%20car%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20play%20golf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Toronto%2C%20I'd%20go%20grocery%20shopping%20in%20a%20sweatsuit%2C%20but%20here%2C%20everybody's%20in%20Alo%20tights%20and%20an%20Alo%20tank%20top.%20It's%20motivation%2C%20though%2C%20seeing%20all%20the%20fit%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20strongest%2C%20mentally%20healthiest%20time%20I've%20felt%20in%20my%20adult%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2280696188-7b4f-4e26-a5fe-fa5a3c080a6e%5C%22%3EI've%20felt%20homesick%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20relocation%20regrets%20yet%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20entire%20life%20is%20so%20different%20when%20you%20move.%20That's%20a%20really%20big%20aspect%20of%20homesickness%20I%20didn't%20think%20of%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20walk%20out%20the%20door%2C%20and%20everything%20is%20different.%20Your%20dentist%20is%20different%2C%20your%20doctor%20is%20different%2C%20your%20hair%20salon%20is%20different%2C%20and%20your%20favorite%20coffee%20shop%20is%20different.%20I%20feel%20guilty%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-deal-with-homesickness-loneliness-living-abroad-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeeling%20homesick%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20should%20be%20so%20happy%20because%20I%20know%20this%20is%20a%20big%20privilege%20and%20a%20blessing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20one%20of%20the%20positives%20of%20moving%20to%20Miami%20with%20my%20husband%20is%20that%20we've%20always%20been%20a%20couple%20that%20likes%20to%20travel%20together.%20Moving%20to%20a%20new%20country%20where%20you%20know%20nobody%20has%20made%20us%20the%20type%20of%20close%20that%20I%20never%20thought%20we%20would%20be.%20I%20didn't%20think%20anyone%20could%20ever%20be%20this%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20strengthened%20our%20connection%20as%20husband%20and%20wife%2C%20and%20that's%20helped%20with%20the%20adjustment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20plan%20out%20your%20life%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20in%20advance.%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20life%20is%20going%20to%20bring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20leave%20Toronto%20because%20I%20didn't%20like%20it.%20I%20left%20because%20there%20were%20better%20opportunities%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20live%20this%20lifestyle%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20we're%20really%20living%20each%20day%20to%20the%20fullest.%20Do%20I%20foresee%20hard%20times%20and%20challenges%3F%20Of%20course.%20But%20ultimately%2C%20I%20still%20remember%20why%20we%20came%20here%2C%20and%20for%20that%20reason%2C%20I%20do%20not%20think%20I'll%20regret%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-moved-to-florida-leaving-canada-cant-work-happier-healthier-2024-5%5C