p%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20ex-husband%20and%20I%20started%20thinking%20about%20getting%20a%20divorce%20in%202007.%20It%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-advice-for-amicable-easy-simple-divorce-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etotally%20amicable%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20we%20just%20knew%20that%20our%20relationship%20wasn't%20one%20that%20was%20going%20to%20last%20forever.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20we%20were%20living%20in%20a%20large%20house%20with%20our%20three%20children%2C%20the%20youngest%20of%20whom%20was%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20major%20economic%20crisis%20going%20on%20and%20we%20weren't%20in%20a%20position%20to%20sell%20the%20house%20and%20buy%20two%20separate%20properties.%20We%20were%20still%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20making%20the%20final%20decision%20if%20we%20were%20going%20to%20officially%20get%20a%20divorce.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbird-nesting-divorce-parenting-plan-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eterm%20%26quot%3Bnesting%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20keeping%20the%20kids%20in%20the%20same%20family%20home%20while%20the%20parents%20move%20in%20and%20out%20%E2%80%94%20wasn't%20one%20we%20had%20ever%20heard%20of%2C%20but%20given%20finances%20and%20our%20indecision%20about%20splitting%2C%20it%20was%20how%20we%20decided%20to%20go%20about%20our%20separation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b1581f4b-55de-4efc-a53f-001cfcb38f7f%5C%22%3EWe%20decided%20to%20try%20nesting%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20house%20was%20large%2C%20we%20started%20by%20taking%20different%20bedrooms%20in%20the%20house%20and%20splitting%20our%20time%20with%20the%20kids.%20I%20would%20do%20the%20morning%20routine%20with%20the%20kids%20one%20day%2C%20and%20he%20would%20do%20the%20next.%20For%20a%20year%2C%20this%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20we%20started%20meeting%20with%20a%20mediator%20and%20lawyer%20to%20finalize%20the%20divorce%2C%20we%20decided%20it%20would%20be%