0is%20expected%20to%20fly%20out%20to%20New%20York%20in%20the%20early%20morning%20of%20May%2030th.%20The%20BCCI%20has%20agreed%20to%20his%20request%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20BCCI%20official%20told%20the%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20T20%20World%20Cup%20is%20being%20jointly%20hosted%20by%20the%20USA%20and%20the%20West%20Indies%20from%20June%202%20to%20June%2029.%20The%20Indian%20cricket%20team%2C%20which%20has%20departed%20India%20for%20New%20York%2C%20will%20begin%20its%20campaign%20against%20Ireland%20on%20June%205%20at%20the%20newly-constructed%20Nassau%20County%20International%20Cricket%20Stadium%20in%20New%20York.%20India%20will%20face%20arch-rivals%20Pakistan%20on%20June%209%2C%20followed%20by%20matches%20against%20co-hosts%20USA%20(June%2012)%20and%20Canada%20(June%2015)%20in%20their%20Group%20A%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20won%20the%20inaugural%20edition%20way%20back%20in%202007%20in%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECricket%20is%20not%20a%20mainstream%20sport%20in%20the%20US%2C%20which%20has%20traditionally%20been%20a%20baseball%2C%20American%20football%2C%20basketball%2C%20ice%20hockey%2C%20and%20soccer-playing%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20diaspora%20from%20the%20Indian%20sub-continent%20as%20well%20as%20those%20belonging%20to%20other%20cricket-playing%20nations%20such%20as%20the%20West%20Indies%20and%20Australia%20play%20the%20sport%20in%20the%20US%20but%20usually%20on%20temporary%2C%20make-do%20pitches%20on%20baseball%20fields%2C%20in%20parks%20and%20on%20school%20sports%20fields%20during%20the%20summer%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716713640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ffsaou3rg_virat-kohli-bcci_625x300_23_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fafter-rcb-heartbreak-virat-kohli-likely-to-miss-t20-world-cup-warm-up-game-vs-bangladesh-rep