%94surging%20from%20144%2C000%20registrations%20in%202022%20to%20354%2C000%20in%202023.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20revenue%20being%20generated%2C%20the%20IMF%20revealed%20that%20last%20year%20%E2%80%9C.ai%20domain%20registrations%20generated%20EC%2487%20million.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20must%20be%20noted%20that%20this%20is%2020%20per%20cent%20more%20than%20the%20Anguillan%20government's%20total%20revenue%20generation%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMF%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%202023%20alone%2C%20this%20surge%20in%20.ai%20domain%20registrations%20generated%20EC%2487%20million%20in%20revenue%20(approximately%20%2432%20million)%E2%80%94just%20over%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20government's%20total%20revenue%20for%20the%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20marks%20a%20dramatic%20increase%20from%20previous%20years%20when%20revenue%20from%20.ai%20domain%20registrations%20hovered%20around%205%20per%20cent.%20Looking%20ahead%2C%20the%20government%20expects%20revenue%20from%20.ai%20domain%20registrations%20to%20stabilize%20at%20around%2015%20per%20cent%20of%20total%20government%20revenue%2C%20as%20the%20initial%20rush%20of%20registrations%20gradually%20slows.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMF%20noted%20that%20Anguilla%20is%20heavily%20dependent%20on%20tourism%20activities%20that%20account%20for%2037%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20GDP.%C2%A0%20The%20growing%20trend%20of%20.ai%20domain%20registrations%20is%20now%20playing%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20diversifying%20its%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716710820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fk2bo8ilo_anguilla-generic_625x300_26_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthis-tiny-island-in-the-caribbean-is-making-millions-using-ai-heres-how-5747975%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20advent%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20has%20undoubtedly%20encouraged%20productivit