ders-views-on-digital-india-rightly-stated-%2Farticleshow%2F110436255.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fadnavis%2C%20Shah%20tried%20to%20work%20for%20Gadkari's%20defeat%2C%20claims%20Raut%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716709771000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110436225%2Cimgsize-1359781.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Ffadnavis-shah-tried-to-work-for-gadkaris-defeat-in-ls-polls-claims-sanjay-raut-bjp-hits-back%2Farticleshow%2F110436223.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajnath%20Singh's%20'Back%20Off'%20Reply%20To%20Opposition%20Over%20Agnipath%20Scheme%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDefence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV%20dismissed%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%20that%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20is%20not%20useful%2C%20and%20doubled%20down%20on%20the%20government's%20stand%20that%20the%20four-year%20enlistment%20programme%20will%20benefit%20a%20large%20section%20of%20the%20young%2C%20employable%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20fully%20confident%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20is%20successful%20and%20will%20remain%20so.%20One%20of%20the%20factors%20behind%20starting%20this%20scheme%20is%20to%20bring%20more%20young%20people%20into%20the%20armed%20forces%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%2C%20selected%20candidates%20are%20enrolled%20as%20Agniveers%20for%20a%20four-year%20period.%20On%20completion%20of%20programme%2C%20Agniveers%20will%20return%20to%20the%20society%20as%20disciplined%2C%20dynamic%2C%20motivated%20and%20skilled%20workforce%20for%20employment%20in%20other%20sectors%20to%20pursue%20their%20career%20in%20a%20job%20of%20their%20choice%2C%20according%20to%20the%20government.%20Of%20these%2C%20up%20to%2025%20per%20cent%20of%20Agniveers%20will%20be%20enrolled%20in%20the%20armed%20forces%20as%20regular%20cadre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20other%20factor%20is%20we%20should%20strive%20to%20have%20a%20section%20of%20the%20population%20disciplined%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Agniveers.%20When%20needed%2C%20they%20will%20have%20the%20right%20skills%20to%20help%20out%20in%20the%20frontline%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20told%20NDTV.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20a%20crime%20to%20prepare%20Agniveers%20to%20be%20disciplined%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Opposition's%20allegations%20that%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20would%20harm%20the%20future%20of%20young%20adults%20who%20are%20just%20entering%20the%20workforce%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20assure%20the%20youths%20that%20we%20will%20not%20allow%20anyone%20to%20play%20with%20their%20future.%20An%20Agniveer%20is%20eligible%20from%2018%20years%2C%20and%20will%20remain%20so%20for%20four%20years.%20They%20will%20learn%20new%20skills%2C%20and%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20four%20years%20will%20have%20a%20few%20lakh%20of%20rupees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20any%20of%20them%20wants%20to%20find%20a%20job%2C%20they%20can.%20If%20any%20of%20them%20wants%20to%20enter%20the%20paramilitary%20forces%2C%20they%20can.%20If%20they%20want%20to%20enter%20the%20services%2C%20of%20course%20they%20can.%20We%20have%20even%20kept%20reservations%20for%20them.%20It's%20not%20like%20anyone%20can%20ignore%20them.%20The%20private%20sector%20also%20wants%20to%20hire%20Agniveers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20government%20will%20not%20allow%20anyone%20to%20play%20with%20the%20future%20of%20our%20young%20population.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20strongly%20criticised%20the%20Opposition%20for%20dragging%20the%20military%20into%20an%20election%20campaign%20issue.%20%26quot%3BThey%20(Opposition)%20has%20only%20one%20agenda%20-%20to%20confuse%20citizens.%20They%20should%20not%20play%20politics%20over%20Agniveers%20and%20the%20military%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20contested%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Lucknow%20constituency%20this%20time%20again.%20He%20had%20won%20from%20there%20twice.%20Lucknow%20is%20a%20prestigious%20seat%20previously%20represented%20by%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20BJP%20retained%20power%20in%202019%2C%20with%20an%20even%20larger%20seat%20share%20than%20in%202014.%20Mr%20Singh%20remained%20one%20of%20the%20key%20members%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20cabinet%20and%20was%20given%20charge%20of%20the%20Defence%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20in%20mind%20the%20spirit%20of%20'Make%20in%20India'%20and%20'Aatmanirbhar%20Bharat'%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20banned%20the%20import%20of%20101%20defence-related%20items%20in%202020.%20In%20May%202021%2C%20he%20decided%20that%20108%20military%20weapons%20and%20systems%2C%20including%20next-generation%20corvettes%2C%20airborne%20early%20warning%20systems%2C%20tank%20engines%20and%20radars%20would%20be%20entirely%20made%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716708600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fbq5oplh8_rajnath-singh-ndtv_625x300_26_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-rajnath-singhs-back-off-reply-to-opposition-on-playing-politics-over-agnipath-scheme-5748197%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV%20dismissed%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%20that%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20is%20not%20useful.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-rajnath-singhs-back-off-reply-to-opposition-on-playing-politics-over-agnipath-scheme-5748197%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F