%20anytime%20and%20anywhere.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Manish%20has%20set%20up%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20telemedicine%20centres%20and%20onboarded%20over%201%2C700%20veterinarians%20and%20para%20veterinarians%20in%2016%20states%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Punjab%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Assam%2C%20Meghalaya%2C%20Manipur%2C%20Mizoram%2C%20Nagaland%2C%20Tripura%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20conducts%20over%202%2C500%20telemedical%20consultancy%20calls%20per%20day%20and%20charges%20Rs%2090%20for%20a%20consultation%20with%20the%20expert%20whereas%20Rs%20150%20for%20a%20field%20visit%2C%20which%20Manish%20says%20is%20more%20than%20double%20the%20market%20which%20charges%20Rs%20300-500.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20he%20has%20also%20designed%20Radio%20Frequency%20Identification%20(RFID)%20tags%20to%20monitor%20and%20trace%20the%20health%2C%20location%2C%20and%20movement%20of%20livestock.%20It%20also%20stores%20prescriptions%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F260896%2Fodisha-balaram-sahu-free-doctor-treatment-cow-cattle-diseases-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisease%20history%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20the%20cattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20Verdant%20Impact%20is%20associated%20with%20more%20than%20six%20lakh%20farmers.%20Of%20this%2C%20more%20than%201.7%20lakh%20are%20directly%20benefitting%20through%20teleconsultations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20his%20work%2C%20Manish%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAmong%20the%20major%20health%20issues%20in%20livestock%20were%20productivity%20and%20difficulties%20in%20pregnancies%20owing%20to%20malnutrition.%20We%20provide%20herbal%20treatment%20that%20boosts%20suitable%20ovulation%20period%20in%20cattle.%E2%80