fed%20hearty%20lunches%20and%20dinners%20by%20his%20wife%20Varada%2C%20where%20(you%20guessed%20it)%20mango%20is%20the%20hero.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20firm%20believer%20that%20one%20must%20know%20what%20they%20are%20consuming%2C%20Ganesh%20treats%20his%20guests%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F349604%2Fhow-to-grow-japanese-mango-miyazaki-at-home-in-odisha-engineer-garden-with-rare-flower-fruit-plants-1000-petal-lotus%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elesson%20in%20mango%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20tracing%20the%20sapling%E2%80%99s%20journey%20right%20from%20seed%20to%20fruit.%20What%E2%80%99s%20more%20is%20that%20you%20can%20even%20live%20in%20a%20mud%20room%20whilst%20at%20the%20farm%2C%20and%20experience%20an%20authentic%20farm%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20the%20journey%20of%20setting%20up%20this%20homestay%20that%20falls%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Ratnagiri%20and%20Sindhudurg%20districts%2C%2042-year-old%20Ganesh%20says%2C%20it%20is%20a%20culmination%20of%20a%20sustainable%20dream.%20He%20credits%20his%20father%20with%20sowing%20the%20seeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-7-1715946426.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mangoes%20are%20the%20hero%20at%20the%20Ganesh%20Agro%20Tourism%20homestay%20in%20Ratnagiri%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-7-1715946426.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-7-1715946426-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-7-1715946426-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploa