the%20productivity%20of%20farmers%20increased%20to%2075%20percent%2C%20she%20shares%2C%20and%20the%20villagers%E2%80%99%20belief%20in%20her%20was%20strengthened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20was%20a%20%3Cem%3Esarpanch%3C%2Fem%3E%20who%20kept%20their%20word.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20Rajawat%E2%80%99s%20good%20work.%20In%202010%2C%20she%20also%20spearheaded%20a%20sanitation%20campaign%20through%20which%20she%20began%20raising%20funds%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F210236%2Ffree-ladies-public-toilet-pune-clean-safe-review-ti-old-buses-innovation-ang136%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econstruction%20of%20toilets%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Her%20strategy%20was%20bold%20and%20unique.%20%E2%80%9CI%20knocked%20on%20the%20door%20of%20every%20home%20and%20told%20the%20beneficiaries%20that%20they%20had%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20project.%20I%20added%20that%20if%20they%20did%20not%20have%20the%20money%2C%20they%20could%20contribute%20their%20time%20to%20dig%20the%20pits.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECreating%20a%20sense%20of%20ownership%20went%20a%20long%20way.%20While%20Rajawat%20insists%20that%20these%20developments%20are%20tiny%20in%20the%20larger%20scheme%20of%20things%2C%20she%20emphasises%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20progress%20of%20a%20country%20is%20equal%20to%20the%20progress%20of%20each%20of%20its%20citizens.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716206876000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSarpanch-Chhavi-with-the-goat_11zon-1715862357.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D350255%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Under%20the%20leadership%20of%20former%20sarpanch%20Chhavi%20Rajawat%2C%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Soda%20Village%20saw%20improved%20infrastructure%2C%20which%20transformed%20the%20community.%20Today%2